:: \ \[EDITED(Routing)\]No thank you. I have other things to worry about. (+1sus) {"position":"1350,475","size":"100,100"}
""At this time, what could possibly be your priority over our holy rapture?! We must stay here and worship, as ordered by our most holy ascendants!""

[["Really, I must be going"|Step away. (+1 sus)]]
[[[EDITED(new)] "You're right - I'll stay."]]


:: ""/How willing would you be to part with that knife of yours?\\"" {"position":"375,1700","size":"100,100"}
USED TWICE

"\"You hear it's call too, huh? As long as that's what it is, I could be persuaded. As long as you don't plan to turn it on me."\"

[["\"I won'\t. I'm not even sure what I need it for, but I don't plan on hurting you.\""]]


:: "Attack the Cannibal" {"position":"500,1950","size":"100,100"}
(Cannibal Fight minigame)

[[Win]]
[[Loss]]


:: "Yes, that's it! I have such a hard time remembering the beginning. Is there any way I can trouble you for that page of yours? {"position":"1700,875","size":"100,100"}
"Oh dear, but this page is important to me! It was the passage I would read my grandson before bed every night. Of course, since he isn't coming with us, I suppose I could give it to you. But first, I must know if you are truly dedicated to following Her below."

[[[EDITED(Routing)] Of course I am! I have wished to be embraced in her ancient arms for as long as I can remember. (+1sus)]]
[[Of course I am! I have wished to be embraced in her ancient tendrils for as long as I can remember.]]
[[[EDITED (Routing)] Of course I am! I have wished to be embraced in her ancient fins for as long as I can remember.(+1sus)]]


:: "\\"Are you... eating those bodies?\\"" {"position":"450,1400","size":"100,100"}
"\"What does it look like, little ghost? We all have our vices. Why do you think I aim to become an ascendant? While we wait though, my desires must be satiated. You wouldn't want me to start feasting on the living, would you?\""

"A horrible grin splits the cannibal's face in two. His question seemed rhetorical, yet he still looks to you eagerly. He twirls the knife in his hand."

(Parasite speaking, red text)
"YOU NEED HIS BLADE"

[[""/How willing would you be to part with that knife of yours?\""]]



:: "\\"I can certainly try.\\"" {"position":"200,1900","size":"100,100"}



:: "\\"I won'\\t. I'm not even sure what I need it for, but I don't plan on hurting you.\\"" {"position":"375,1825","size":"100,100"}
"\"I know what you need it for. What's more important is the key to the door over there. It'll call you there sooner or later.\""

"The cannibal hands you the dull blade."
(Add knife to player inventory)

"\"Tell you what. You make this morsel here a bit more palateable, and it's yours. The prisoners down here were oh so stressed. Bad for the flesh.\""
(Add arm to player inventory)

[["\"I can certainly try.\""]] (Leave dialogue)
[["Attack the Cannibal"]]


