:: Attempt to search your memories once more. {"position":"550,400","size":"100,100"}
Against all instinct, you rage through your migraine-bordering headache. Single, isolated images drip into your consciousness like water from unserviced faucet.

A masked man.
His reaching hand.
The boarding of a boat.

That is all you can glean for now. It may be best to attempt to remember more from your surroundings.

[[Open your eyes. |Attempt to gain your bearings.]]


:: Click on book {"position":"975,775","size":"100,100"}
The book is open to a torn and yellowed page with few words written on it. You don't have nearly enough time or interest for that matter to read through it. 

The half of the page that remains bound to the rest of the book reads, " -iver us, for we yearn to be entangled in your cold emabrace as the children of your new earth."

((Red text, parasite speaking) You need the rest of this."


:: Click on crates {"position":"625,625","size":"100,100"}
They're bolted shut. There's no way to tell what might be in them.


:: Click on dead bodies {"position":"500,625","size":"100,100"}
Disgusting. They smell far too awful to even consider getting closer than you already are, much less to consider what happened to them.


:: Click on paraphenalia {"position":"850,625","size":"100,100"}
At a glance, you thought someone had set up a Catholic gift shop in the corner. Upon further inspection, you realize nothing could be further from the truth. There are effigies and symbols the likes of which you have never seen.

[[Click on statuette]]
[[Click on book]]
[[Click on pendant]]
[[Click on poster]]


:: Click on pendant {"position":"600,775","size":"100,100"}
A small silver pendant depicting multiple small tendrils.

Perhaps the god these people follow has tentacles or feelers.


:: Click on poster {"position":"725,775","size":"100,100"}
The worn, tattered poster reads "GLORY TO THE ONE BELOW" along the top. Along the bottom, it reads, "AND MAY SHE RETURN ABOVE".


Maybe this is some sort of anachronism or call and response. You shudder to think what kind of being they might be referring to.


:: Click on rack {"position":"825,1375","size":"100,100"}
(Add spices and herbs to inventory.)


:: Click on statuette {"position":"850,775","size":"100,100"}
A small copper statue of what, at first glance, appears to be a robed man. Upon further inspection, the man seems to have a fish-like head and webbed fingers.

You wonder whether this is their god or one of them, and how such a form could be seen as worthy of worship.


:: Click on the Cabinets {"position":"825,1250","size":"100,100"}
(Cabinets open)

"They're full of dead fish. It smells like nothing you've ever experiences. You've never had a gag reflex, but you seem to have found one. A small rack of spices and herbs sits on the lowermost shelf."

[[Click on rack]]


:: Click on the Cutting board {"position":"525,1250","size":"100,100"}
(If the player does not have the arm )

"A small wooden cutting board with countless knife marks in it. You're not sure who's blood stains the surface, and you're not sure you want to."

(If the player has diced the arm but has not cooked it)

"You've mutilated the arm plenty. It should be able to be cooked at this point."

(If the player has the arm but has not yet diced it)

"A cutting board. You can use this to cut the arm into smaller pieces."

(Add diced flesh and bone to inventory)
-> BEGIN CUTTING BOARD MINIGAME


:: Click on the Door {"position":"1125,1250","size":"100,100"}
(if player does not yet have the key)

(Inner monologue) "It's locked."

(If the player has the key)

"A locked door, for which you have the key. Enter?"

[[Enter the door.]]


:: Click on the Man {"position":"375,1250","size":"100,100"}
"A lithe, gangly man sits above a nigh-unrecognizable pile of bodies."

"\"Hey! Snuck up on me a little there... most people would have a little more self-preservation than to sneak up on a stranger like that. What brings you here, little ghost?\""

[["\"I'm... not sure. I can't remember. I just sort of woke up here.\""]]
[["\"Are you... eating those bodies?\""]]
[["\"I'm one of you. I aim to reach Her, and ascend my body.""(+1 sus)]]



:: Click on the Pot {"position":"675,1250","size":"100,100"}
(If player does not have the arm)

"A small, tarnished, cast iron pot full of water."

(If player has the arm but has not diced it yet)

"A small, tarnished, cast iron pot full of water. I could stew the arm in this, but it's far too large to fit."

(If player has the arm and has diced it, but does not have the spices.)

"A small, tarnished, cast iron pot full of water. I could stew the arm meat in this, but I should probably find something else to add first."

(If player has both the arm and the spices.)

"A small, tarnished, cast iron pot full of water. I can make a stew in this with the ingredients I've gathered."

->BEGIN COOKING MINIGAME


